node.text: A few moments from Holi Festival deep in the crowds of Vrindavan (the birth place of Holi) It was so much fun being able to be a part of India’s craziest festival of the year, this is just a quick glimpse of the trip and I’ll be posting some vlog style videos from India real soon so stay tuned! 🙏🏼🇮🇳 Shot and experienced this with 2 legends @jacob @danielsjensen

node.title: Deep inside India’s craziest festival of the year - The Holi Festival 🇮🇳

node.text:
Barcelona photo dump week one, mostly iPhone shots 🇪🇸
After 3 weeks in Ibiza I needed a detox, so I flew out to BCN last minute to spend a week here eating healthy, getting back into a fitness routine and catching up on work. I love this place so much that I already extended an extra 10 days 🙌🏼

node.text:
One rule at the @twojeys villa, everyone has to paint the half pipe 🎨 
What a time I’ve had at this place, made new friends for life and had some of my best ever memories.
3 weeks on this island has definitely taken its toll 💀 tomorrow I’m leaving Ibiza and flying out to one of my favourite cities, Barcelona 🙌🏼

node.text:
We took the yacht out to Formentera for the day 💦
Spent the day hanging with friends, whipping around on jet skis, eating good food and swimming in the sea. The yacht was booked with @buckingham_lloyds - they get priority on yacht bookings which is really handy as the majority are often fully booked in high season 🛥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JACK MORRIS in Ibiza, Spain with @doyoutravel, @buckingham_lloyds, and @dytpresets. May be an image of body of water.

node.text:
Good morning from Ibizaaa 🇪🇸
I’ve been starting each day with a morning walk along the coast followed by a dip in the pool!
How nice is this view from the @buckingham_lloyds villa 🤤

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by JACK MORRIS on July 12, 2021 tagging @doyoutravel, @buckingham_lloyds, and @dytpresets. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
London to Ibiza - First time ever flying on a private jet 😅✔️
@buckingham_lloyds asked me to go all out on trying their services, and their services are almost limitless haha. I asked to fly out on the P jet and they said yes, so here I am on my way to Ibiza from London.
B&L only partner with jets that offset their carbon footprint, so even when catering to those that travel in this style, sustainability is still in mind.
I’ve only been to Ibiza once before and didn’t really get to see the place properly so it kinda feels like my first time. Hit me up with any recommendations please! 🚀

node.text:
My last morning in the UK before flying out to Ibiza today!
This time in London I stayed in a different @buckingham_lloyds apartment, I loved that this one had a balcony facing Hyde Park, perfect for my morning coffee! ☕️
If you’re planing a trip to London, then you can use code DOYOUTRAVEL20 for 20% off rates with Buckingham Lloyds, for both quarantine or regular trips! 🙌🏼

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by JACK MORRIS in Rivington with @doyoutravel, and @dytpresets. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text:
I’ve not seen my mum and dad since 2019 so it’s been so nice being back in my home town for the last couple of days!
I had to cut this trip short but I’ll be back here for longer next month 😍
I’m heading back to London now for the weekend, then Ibiza on Sunday! 🚀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by JACK MORRIS on July 07, 2021 tagging @doyoutravel, and @dytpresets. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Feels good to be back in the UK! 🇬🇧 This morning I took a stroll around Notting Hill before jumping on a train to Manchester, here’s a few snaps.
It’s my first time being back in the UK / seeing my family since 2019!
Excited to be back in the north of England for the next couple of nights before heading back to London on Friday 🚀

node.text:
Just posted my East Java video on YouTube! @tropicfeel asked me to ‘Say Yes’ and go on a last minute adventure somewhere in Indonesia. I picked East Java to hike the Ijen Volcano at sunrise.

Tropicfeel want to invite you to ‘Say Yes’ too! They’re hosting a big giveaway now so that you can go on your own adventure, check it out now on their IG! This album is a collection of moments captured during that trip. #sayyes
